column5: I have nothing to do with the store or the reel company. THIS IS NOT SPAM  Just a video of the reel and how sweet it is.    I had the Black betty in my hands today. The Concept is much better. JMO here.
whats the price on those contraptions?  looks like a nice reel but ive never used that style before
$54.94 at LeBaron  Hey Daniel  I cant find it on their site? Got a link dude?

http://www.lebaron.ca/pdf_files_fall12/rapala_ice_combos.pdf  here you go   Thank you.  I cant believe that the R rods have gone up in price. They are a real nice rod,but come on.  May have to grab one of those 36-42 ice locker bags. Nice deal.

Hey Daniel  I cant find it on their site? Got a link dude?  I find Rapala Canada has lots of neat stuff that they don't get in the USA. Always make sure you search the Canadian site for their products.
